assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Al-Enma'a Real Estate Company K.S.C.P. engages in the contracting, management, and maintenance of real estate primarily in Kuwait, the Gulf Countries, and internationally. The company operates through Construction Projects, Services Rendered, Real Estate, and Investments segments. The Construction Projects segment undertakes contracts to construct buildings, such as commercial, residential, industrial, and touristic. The Services Rendered segment engages in the maintenance of mechanical and electrical spare parts, and building materials. This segment also provides security services and manages real estate for others. The Real Estate segment manages its properties and rents properties for others. The Investments segment participates and invests in shares of local and foreign companies and real estate properties. It also provides transportation service for funds and precious metals. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Kuwait City, Kuwait. Al-Enma'a Real Estate Company K.S.C.P. is a subsidiary of Kuwait Finance House K.S.C.P.
